INSERT INTO `Blog` VALUES (1741, '2024-01-30 06:34:18.745', '2019-05-24 02:36:33.000', '2024-01-30 06:34:18.745', '唐伯虎道：“人生七十古稀，我年七十为奇。前十年幼小，后十年衰老；中间止有五十年，一半又在夜里过了。算来止有二十五年在世，受尽多少奔波烦恼。”只要一日平安，就是人间好光景。所谓居安思危，并非焦虑未来，而是珍惜眼下<img alt=\"[给你小心心]\" title=\"[给你小心心]\" src=\"https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/ca/qixi2018_xiaoxinxin_org.png\" /><img alt=\"[给你小心心]\" title=\"[给你小心心]\" src=\"https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/ca/qixi2018_xiaoxinxin_org.png\" /><img alt=\"[给你小心心]\" title=\"[给你小心心]\" src=\"https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/ca/qixi2018_xiaoxinxin_org.png\" />', 0, 1);
INSERT INTO `Blog` VALUES (1742, '2024-01-30 06:34:18.749', '2019-05-23 14:26:23.000', '2024-01-30 06:34:18.749', '完了，又到了一出门就回不了家的季节了<img alt=\"[允悲]\" title=\"[允悲]\" src=\"https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/83/2018new_kuxiao_org.png\" />夏天的夜晚实在太舒服了，精神实在是太抖擞了，完全么有办法在桌前学习，只想到处嗨<img alt=\"[泪]\" title=\"[泪]\" src=\"https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/6e/2018new_leimu_org.png\" />应该雇个人天天看着我学习，以及督促我挣钱，再这么下去彻底成散人了<img alt=\"[跪了]\" title=\"[跪了]\" src=\"https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/75/2018new_gui_org.png\" /><img alt=\"[跪了]\" title=\"[跪了]\" src=\"https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/75/2018new_gui_org.png\" />分享Bryan Adams 的歌曲 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://weibo.com/p/10151501_62338488\"><img class=\"icon-link\" src=\"https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_music_default.png\"/>Summer Of 69 (Album Version)</a> ​​​', 0, 1);
