INSERT INTO `Blog` VALUES (2047, '2024-01-30 06:35:13.666', '2019-01-13 05:46:00.000', '2024-01-30 06:35:13.666', '今天腊八，去大觉寺祈福。半路想上厕所，停车跑临近的村里找了半天，耽误了二十多分钟，到的时候粥刚发完<img alt=\"[允悲]\" title=\"[允悲]\" src=\"https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/83/2018new_kuxiao_org.png\" />……不过我早上在家也喝啦，还好。祝大家吉祥如意哈<img alt=\"[心]\" title=\"[心]\" src=\"https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/8a/2018new_xin_org.png\" />🙏🙏  ​​​', 0, 1);
